## --- Project Specific Exclusions ---
# Ignore the actual memory dumps (often very large)
*.exe
*.bin
*.dmp
!ExtractKeysFromDump.exe # Optional: Un-comment if you want to track the actual tool binary

# Ignore extracted key files to prevent leaking them
*.dat

